00:18:18.600 --> 00:18:20.400
You know, those chemicals
were replicating,

00:18:20.400 --> 00:18:22.050
in effect, over there.

00:18:22.050 --> 00:18:23.400
No, reproducing takes work.

00:18:23.400 --> 00:18:26.310
So we have to explain
