00:18:41.040 --> 00:18:42.690
And yet, I'm gone.

00:18:42.690 --> 00:18:45.720
So I have to be able
to explain that and not

00:18:45.720 --> 00:18:48.224
resort to phantoms,
not resort to ghosts.

00:18:48.224 --> 00:18:49.140
This is the challenge.

00:18:49.140 --> 00:18:52.290
