00:45:55.430 --> 00:45:56.960
over openings and closings.

00:45:56.960 --> 00:45:59.990
That is, several generations
down the line, one

00:45:59.990 --> 00:46:05.030
of these seeds may have
no molecules in continuity

00:46:05.030 --> 00:46:07.030
with the original one.

00:46:07.030 --> 00:46:08.030
And it's not the energy.

00:46:08.030 --> 00:46:10.700
The energy's coming
from the outside.

00:46:10.700 --> 00:46:13.850
What is being lost
is the constraint.

00:46:13.850 --> 00:46:19.670
When I die, my molecules are
free to do way more things.

00:46:19.670 --> 00:46:22.400
Life is not an add-on to
physics and chemistry.

00:46:22.400 --> 00:46:23.240
It's a subset.

00:46:23.240 --> 00:46:25.760
It's a self-constrained
subset, that

00:46:25.760 --> 00:46:27.890
is, me reducing
the possibilities

00:46:27.890 --> 00:46:29.090
as long as I live.

00:46:29.090 --> 00:46:33.980
And as the synergies, by
now, through evolution, I've

00:46:33.980 --> 00:46:36.500
accumulated vast
quantities of synergies,

00:46:36.500 --> 00:46:38.820
like the one we started
